Word-list attribution and licensing
====================================

Solution lists (CC BY-SA 4.0)
-----------------------------

The solution lists shipped in `data/solutions-en.js` and
`data/solutions-de.js` are derived from the hermitdave/FrequencyWords
frequency lists, which are built from the OpenSubtitles corpus. The list
content is licensed under Creative Commons Attribution-ShareAlike 4.0
International (CC BY-SA 4.0). These derived solution lists are made
available under the same CC BY-SA 4.0 license.

  Source:  https://github.com/hermitdave/FrequencyWords
  License: https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by-sa/4.0/

Valid-guess lists (no attribution required)
-------------------------------------------

The valid-guess lists derive from ENABLE (public domain) for English and
from enz/german-wordlist (CC0) for German. Public domain and CC0 sources
require no attribution; they are named here for provenance only.
